import React from 'react'; function Projects() { return (

Our Projects

Here are some of the projects we have worked on:

  • Project 1: Bio-Sensor for Environmental Monitoring

    A bio-sensor designed to detect and monitor environmental pollutants in real-time. This project aims to provide a cost-effective and efficient solution for environmental protection.

  • Project 2: Synthetic Biology for Sustainable Agriculture

    Developing genetically engineered crops that are resistant to pests and diseases, and can thrive in harsh environmental conditions. This project aims to improve food security and sustainability.

  • Project 3: Personalized Medicine through Synthetic Biology

    Creating personalized treatment plans for patients based on their genetic makeup. This project aims to revolutionize healthcare by providing targeted and effective treatments.
